title: Factory Worker Medium Light Skin Tone
description: A person working in a factory, often depicted in protective gear like a hard hat. Represents industrial work, personufacturing, and labor.
apple_vendor_description: The factory worker emoji on Apple devices presents a professional with a determined yet approachable expression, rendered with medium-light skin tone and Apple's signature 3D realism.  Clad in a practical uniform with subtle fabric textures and realistic lighting, this emoji embodies hard work, industry, and dedication.  It's a versatile symbol for occupations in manufacturing, labor, or any role involving diligent effort.
